    "whatItDoes": "Fetches and parses Hugging Face paper pages using arXiv IDs or HF paper URLs. Returns full paper content as markdown or structured metadata including authors, linked models, datasets, spaces, GitHub repos, and project pages. Covers both the papers API and the daily papers feed.",
